### LEVEL 2 — INPUT FILE GENERATOR

**⚠️ Needs recreation by founder before use.**

Triggered when: founder attaches `region_cluster_file.json` and specifies one post to research.

Single mode only. Always reads the cluster file. One post per run. Never batch.

Research phases:
1. Extract all constraints from cluster file — primary keyword locked, do-not-use list active
2. SERP competitor analysis — what ranks now, what it misses, where the gap is
3. Business owner intelligence — who they are, their pain, their exact language, their emotional state
4. Semantic keyword research — cleared against keyword do-not-use list
5. Stat block research — 3 real credibility stats from real sources
6. FAQ research — real objections from real business owner communities
7. H2 structure — built from real pain points and exact search phrases
8. Internal link mapping — run last, after all research is complete

Output: `business_post_input_file.json` — single source of truth for the Post Writer. 1500-2000 words max. Includes writer instructions in every section.

